"—	Step the First: Consecrate the body with the Blessings of Tu'whacca.\n"
"\n"
"—	Step the Second: Remove all internal organs before they can decay, causing "
"unsightly stains.\n"
"\n"
"—	Step the Third: Remove all brain tissue. This is to be done through the "
"nostrils using the hook-spoons, so as to avoid damaging the skin of face and "
"head.\n"
"\n"
