"placing packets of parch-salt within its cavities.\n"
"\n"
"—	Step the Fifth: Replace lost volume within the body with inert material, "
"paying special attention to restoring the features of the face. \n"
"\n"
"—	Step the Sixth: The layers of wrapping: wrap the body in one hundred paces "
"of linen, then coat the linen with warm juniper resin. Do this three times. \n"
"\n"
"—	Step the Seventh: The adorning of amulets: array the body in amulets and "
"bracelets that represent the station of the body in life. \n"
"\n"
